cs.SD, cs.CV, cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG 

The paper proposes an audio-visual deep CNN SE model, which incorporates audio and visual streams into a unified network model. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the following sub-categories: 

- cs.SD (Sound)
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition)
- cs.SD (Speech and Signal Processing)
- cs.CL (Computation and Language)
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
